@page "/adminDashboard"

<div class="container mt-4" style="max-width: 900px;">
	<div class="card shadow-sm">
		<div class="card-header bg-primary text-white">
			<h4 class="mb-0 text-center text-white">Alien Administration Page</h4>
		</div>
		<div class="card-body">
			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-md-5">
					<img src="images/admin.png" class="img-fluid rounded-start" alt="Administrator Photo" />
				</div>
				<div class="col-md-7 d-flex align-items-start">
					<div class="card-body">
						<h3 class="card-title text-white bg-primary">👽Admin Zorbflax Quibloxon-7👽</h3>
						<p class="card-text text-dark">
							<strong>Greetings, Earth Ally!</strong> Welcome to the Galactic Alien Administration Portal — the universe's most secure and slightly chaotic hub for interstellar logistics and facility coordination!
						</p>
						<p class="card-text text-dark">
							Zorbflax, or "Zorbie" as his colleagues call him, comes from the twin moons of <em>Glarnok-5</em>, known for its extreme bureaucracy and even more extreme plasma puddings.
						</p>
						<p class="card-text text-dark">
							A graduate of the <strong>Intergalactic Institute of Administrative Order</strong>, Zorbflax has spent the last 400 Earth-years making sure aliens land in comfort, style, and the correct timezone. His favorite Earth activity? Watching tourists try to interpret alien restroom signs.
						</p>
						<p class="card-text text-dark">
							If the blue light next to his name is blinking, don’t worry — he’s just actively watching spreadsheets. Probably.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

